with mock.patch('propargs.data_store._open_file_as_json'
    ) as mock_open_file_as_json:
    mock_open_file_as_json.return_value = json.loads(
        '{{ "{prop_name}": {{"val": 7}} }}'.format(prop_name=DUMMY_PROP_NM))
    prop_args.ds_file = 'some_file'
    data_store.set_props_from_ds(prop_args)
    assert prop_args[DUMMY_PROP_NM] == 7
